ctivity that primarily serves to encourage recreational or business travel in or to the United States, including activities relating to public or nonprofit entertainment venues in the United States.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbc724744-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s3122/16"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"16"},"text":"(16)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" United States","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The term “United States” means all of the States.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbc724745-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s3122/17"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"17"},"text":"(17)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" University center","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The term “university center” means an institution of higher education or a consortium of institutions of higher education established under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s3147/c/1"},"text":"section 3147(c)(1) of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idbc724746-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/136/s3"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–136, § 3","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/393/tI/s102/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–393, title I, § 102(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1998-11-13"},"text":"Nov. 13, 1998","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/112/3599"},"text":"112 Stat. 3599","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"r